{"tid":1966423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"修咸頓延遲發放薪金 成英超首例","createTime":"2020-04-10T07:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T09:04:46.000Z","uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2ba2c7882e3b74afc31ffe55bb37bdc6bf07ed","tid":1966423,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=387384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387384&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6zKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=62264369\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387384&h=dca31686\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=387384</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】英超聯的修咸頓成為第一支延遲發放薪金的英超球會。<br />\n<br />\n修咸頓於官方網站發聲明，由今個月開始連續三個月延遲發放部分薪金，以應付疫情帶來的經濟危機，會方向球員保證，絕對不會拖欠薪金，預計七月就會回復正常，陣中全數一隊球員、教練，以及管理層已經同意相關安排。<br />\n<br />\n英超賽會於早前跟20支球隊代表開會之後，建議球員未來一年減薪三成，協助度過疫情危機，但未能跟球員工會達成共識，部分球會申請英國的疫情補助，支付球員部分薪金，亦惹來批評。"},{"pid":"f4d1772919253a8ecbeb049ca710b1a4b4a079ff","tid":1966423,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">【國際戰線，靠你支持！】</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">頂住人民幣，對抗大外宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>為美國醫護捐贈醫療物資</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowerment-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharity.gofundme.com%2Fo%2Fen%2Fcampaign%2Fmasks-empowerment-campaign&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6zKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=1822dab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowermen